sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as Notification API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant BullMQ as BullMQ Queue
    participant Worker as Notification Worker
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant Push as Push Service
    participant Socket as Socket.IO

    %% Get Notifications
    U->>API: GET /notifications/my
    API->>Redis: Check cache
    Redis-->>API: Cache miss
    API->>DB: Find user notifications
    DB-->>API: Notifications
    API->>Redis: Cache results
    API-->>U: Notifications + pagination

    %% Get Unread Count
    U->>API: GET /notifications/unread-count
    API->>Redis: Check cache
    Redis-->>API: Cache miss
    API->>DB: Count unread
    DB-->>API: Count
    API->>Redis: Cache count (60s TTL)
    API-->>U: Unread count

    %% Mark as Read
    U->>API: POST /notifications/:id/read
    API->>DB: Update status + readAt
    DB-->>API: Updated
    API->>Redis: Invalidate cache
    Redis-->>API: Done
    API-->>U: Success

    %% Mark All as Read
    U->>API: POST /notifications/read-all
    API->>DB: UpdateMany status=read
    DB-->>API: Count updated
    API->>Redis: Invalidate all caches
    API-->>U: Success

    %% Create Notification (Internal)
    Note over API,Worker: Task Assignment Event
    API->>DB: Create notification
    DB-->>API: Created
    API->>BullMQ: Queue job
    BullMQ-->>API: Job queued
    API-->>U: Success

    Note over BullMQ: Async Processing
    BullMQ->>Worker: Process job
    Worker->>DB: Get notification details
    DB-->>Worker: Details
    Worker->>Socket: Emit real-time
    Socket-->>U: Real-time notification

    alt Channel: Email
        Worker->>Email: Send email
        Email-->>Worker: Sent
    end

    alt Channel: Push
        Worker->>Push: Send push
        Push-->>Worker: Sent
    end

    Worker->>DB: Update deliveredAt
    DB-->>Worker: Updated

    %% Schedule Reminder
    U->>API: POST /notifications/schedule-reminder
    API->>DB: Create scheduled notification
    DB-->>API: Created
    API->>BullMQ: Schedule with delay
    BullMQ-->>API: Job scheduled
    API-->>U: Reminder scheduled

    Note over BullMQ: At scheduled time
    BullMQ->>Worker: Process reminder
    Worker->>DB: Get task + user
    DB-->>Worker: Data
    Worker->>Worker: Create notification
    Worker->>U: Send via channels

    %% Bulk Notification (Admin)
    Note over API,Worker: Admin Bulk Send
    Admin->>API: POST /notifications/bulk
    API->>API: Validate (max 1000)
    loop For each userId
        API->>DB: Create notification
        API->>BullMQ: Queue job
    end
    API-->>Admin: Success

    %% Cleanup (Cron)
    Note over Worker: Daily at 2 AM
    Worker->>DB: Delete old notifications
    Note right of Worker: Read: 30 days<br/>Unread: 90 days
    DB-->>Worker: Deleted count
